=== Cross-phase fix: API key mechanism gap (2026-07-09) ===

Discovered during first dogfooding run (§16) against live Metis endpoint.
Config layer gap: AgentConfigFile YAML schema had no api_key field — neither
the frontmatter struct nor the loop.AgentConfig translation layer carried
any credential information.

Fix: added api_key_env (env var name, not key value) to AgentConfigFile YAML
schema, propagated through ToAgentConfig() to loop.AgentConfig.APIKeyEnv,
resolved to the actual key value via os.Getenv in cmd/harness/main.go, and
stored in loop.AgentConfig.APIKey for the turn loop to pass into llm.Request.

Design decision: per-agent env var name (not a single fixed env var) to
support the project's multi-provider-per-agent design — some agents on
Metis, some on local llama.cpp which may need no key at all.

Full design documented in docs/adr-fix-api-key-mechanism.md.
